FY 2026 Plans:
Funding continues OFP development to improve warfighting capabilities for the F-15 fleet; fixes problems with OFP Release 25;
updates F-15 common OFP to include the latest capabilities for highly contested environment, weapons including HACM, LRASM,
FALCO, sensor systems including IRST integration, Eagle Passive Active Warning Survivability System (EPAWSS), and radar
and sensors integration. Initiates planned updates to F-15 training systems to bring concurrent with the F-15 fleet by 4Q FY2027.
