Funding continues OFP development efforts improving war-fighting capabilities for the F-15E and the added capabilities of the
F-15EX fleet. Addresses emergent needs for Long Range Kill Chain and Collaborative Combat Aircraft missions. Integrates new
or improved capabilities enhancing the F-15's ability to engage in highly contested environments, such as Beyond Line-of-Sight

