FY 2026 Plans:
-SABER continues research, development, testing, and evaluation necessary to support upcoming ship installs
to additional platforms.
-SABER will integrate directly with the Combat System enclave aboard FFG 62 class in addition to continued
deployments in the Hull Mechanical and Electrical (HM&E) enclaves.
-The program continues development of automation technologies for software qualification as well as start the
employment of those automation technologies.
-SABER will complete annual updates to enumeration technology tools, additional shipboard controllers, shore-
side lab testing, and shipboard enumerations.
-SABER continues investigation of technologies to handle increased bandwidth in support of maturing enclave
requirements.
-SABER will mature fielded capability to support developing cyber threat requirements including activities related
to updating the program's threat model.

