       Change Summary Explanation
       FUNDING:
       FY2027 budget increased overall by $11.200M from FY2026 budget request. Breakout of impacted programs is below.

       (PU 0734) The FY2027 budget decrease of $5.230M is due to requirement adjustments for the development of modernized capabilities associated with network
