pods for MQ-9 aircraft integration, providing critical capabilities for advanced sensing, platform protection and
mesh network expansion. With the FY 2026 budget submission, funding for these payloads was re-aligned under
the MQ-9 program to facilitate more transparent execution. This update eliminates redundancy and streamlines
program oversight.

