as well as over SATCOM constellations in other orbit regimes. Procure and install additional Joint Hubs (JHs) at additional DoW
SATCOM teleports. Includes the development of requirements, architectures and interfaces to operate over a variety of terminals
and access points. Other covered activities include software development, capability demonstrations, test and integration efforts,
prototype development, program office support, studies, technical analysis, and activities that may leverage commercial, U.S.
Government partnership, and international opportunities.

FY 2026 Plans:
