segments: MMS, KMS and JHs. Integrate these systems into existing Satellite Communications (SATCOM) teleports to enable
PTW operations over WGS satellites. Support the build, test, and installation of hardware required to operate the system at IOC
and FOC.

FY 2026 Plans:
Continue development of software focused on initial capability delivery and develop fixes for discrepancies identified in test and
evaluation activities. Implement system resiliency, cyber resiliency, and crypto standards necessary to operate in the contested
space and cyber domains.
FY 2027 Plans:
Continue development of software focused on initial capability delivery and develop fixes for discrepancies identified in test
and evaluation activities in order to achieve IOC. Continue development to FOC delivery. Implement system resiliency, cyber
resiliency, and crypto standards necessary to operate in the contested space and cyber domains.
