against unique threats. This funding provides programmatic support to update the system including hardware, firmware, and
software to enable the system's ability to detect and defeat a distinct category of threats. Utilizing the latest threat models, the
AFRL DIME, GWEF, and NGC will update detection and defeat software using machine learning, modeling, simulation, and test.


