- Tested and deployed modernized simulation capabilities delivering realistic behavior simulation for current and future Air Tasking
Order (ATO) and C5ISR mission sets with a substantially modernized core Modeling and Simulation (M&S) engine around a
common USAF framework compatible with Air Operation Center operations and modernization




