Title: Transformational Technology Development                                                                                               23.053       0.000           0.000
Description: In FY 2026, the Transformational Technology Development effort and associated funding will transfer within
this Program Element to Project 630321, Space Warfighter Technologist Capabilities, to provide increased transparency and
traceability of USSF S&T Vanguard and WARTECH efforts and activities.

This effort initiates new and continue existing transformational technology development. The Department of the Air Force (DAF)
needs to provide game-changing leap-ahead capabilities to meet future force designs. This effort identifies transformational
science and technology investment opportunities through the WARfighter- TECHnologist (WARTECH) process. The WARTECH
process enables the DAF enterprise to collaboratively translate future force design priorities and requirements into targeted USSF
science and technology investments.

WARTECH accelerates capability development and responds to emerging technology opportunities by supporting integrated
concept exploration. These investments support activities such as mission thread analyses to demonstrate military utility and
software and hardware feasibility assessments. Select efforts will evolve into either a Vanguard Pathfinder to allow for further
assessment and maturation or be designated a Vanguard Prospect or Vanguard indicating enterprise-level priority.

FY 2026 Plans:
In FY 2026, work and associated funding with the Payload Delivery System activity was separated from the Transformational
Technology Development effort and transferred within this Program Element to the Payload Delivery System effort under Project
630321, Space Warfighter Technologist Capabilities. The remaining non-Payload Delivery system work under this effort and
associated funding transferred to Project 630321, Space Warfighter Technologist Capabilities under the Transformational
Technology effort. These transfers provide Congress increased transparency and traceability of USSF S&T Vanguard and
WARTECH efforts and activities.
