D. Acquisition Strategy
In accordance with the Mar 6, 2025 Secretary of Defense (SECDEF) Memo with the subject, "Directing Modern Software Acquisition to Maximize Lethality,” The
Program Executive Officer (PEO) for Operational Test and Training Infrastructure (OTTI) will adopt the Software Acquisition Pathway to rapidly deliver scaled digital
capabilities and evolve the DEE system faster than adversaries can adapt to the battlefield. Additionally, the DEE program office will apply authorities provided under title
10 U.S.C. 167.4022 and maximize use of Commercial Solutions Openings (CSOs), and Other Transactions Authority (OTA), and other contract approaches for acquiring
DEE capabilities.


